2002-04-23  Didier Verna  <didier@lrde.epita.fr>

	* fixme.dtx: fix bug in index handling reported by Knut Lickert
	<knut@lickert.net>: index entries were unconditionally built.
	Use \nobreakspace instead of the tilda character. This avoids
	conflicts with Babel in Spanish environments.

