2000-12-26  Didier Verna  <didier@lrde.epita.fr>

	* fixme.ins: prettyfied the preamble.

        * fink.dtx: prepared for using index and glossary. Added a call to
        `\CharacterTable'. Used the `macro' environment in code
        description. Some documentation changes.
	(final): improved error message passed to \PackageError.

	* README (Changes): new section. It is not worth using index and
        glossary in the dtx file right now.

        * Makefile (clean): also remove index and glossary aux files.
        (distclean): Moved the "-rm -fr $(PROJECT)-*" action to the
        `clean' target.
        (%.sty): answer `y' to LaTeX's question.
        (%.dvi): prepared for using index and glossary.

