	* fixme.dtx: added backslashes to macro names in calls to
	\DescribeMacro.
	Moved the descriptions of \listfixmename to the "Main Macros"
	section, and added a comment in the code.
	Support for german by Harald Harders <h.harders@tu-bs.de>.

